{"id":12720,"date":"2020-09-24T09:57:53","date_gmt":"2020-09-24T09:57:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?page_id=12720"},"modified":"2021-05-18T11:59:21","modified_gmt":"2021-05-18T11:59:21","slug":"zoom-sur-levaluation-de-conformite","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/evaluation-de-la-conformite\/zoom-sur-levaluation-de-conformite\/","title":{"rendered":"Zoom sur l&rsquo;\u00e9valuation de conformit\u00e9"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-6cb7e686ebef98e0fde39775554972bf\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-42e13c8b38b33593601db8cbc127e145\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-f12ef0c8d5d3e2b4f5c2e854690178fa\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-d999bd41334a4b6482c34ef0209c99af\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Zoom sur l&rsquo;\u00e9valuation de la conformit\u00e9<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Au sein de l\u2019AGANOR, l\u2019Evaluation de la Conformit\u00e9 est (constitue) l\u2019un des piliers de l\u2019infrastructure qualit\u00e9 national, contribuant ainsi de mani\u00e8re significative au d\u00e9veloppement du pays, avec pour objectifs\u00a0:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>La protection de la sant\u00e9 et de la sant\u00e9 du consommateur et l\u2019environnement contre des produits non conformes et dangereux ;<\/li>\n<li>La lutte contre la concurrence d\u00e9loyale des produits et services non conformes aux normes ;<\/li>\n<li>L\u2019am\u00e9lioration de la comp\u00e9titivit\u00e9 de l\u2019appareil productif national par l\u2019application des normes permettant d\u2019acc\u00e9der aux diff\u00e9rents march\u00e9s (national, r\u00e9gional et international) ;<\/li>\n<li>La tra\u00e7abilit\u00e9 des produits et services certifi\u00e9s.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Au niveau national, l\u2019Evaluation de la Conformit\u00e9 regroupe trois (3) principales activit\u00e9s\u00a0:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>La Certification ;<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>La cr\u00e9ation et la gestion des Marques et Labels ;<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>La Surveillance du March\u00e9.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":11898,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12720"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=12720"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12720\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14035,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12720\/revisions\/14035"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\